title: 13th Buy - Oct 19
body:
We've setup a Snapshot voting strategy that supports staked Mutant Cats as well as unstaked! We listened to our community - you won't need to pay any gas to unstake and vote.

Now... what should the Mutant Cat DAO buy next?
